{"tid":365862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己啱曬嘅人同我死入嚟","createTime":"2017-08-19T14:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T14:51:28.000Z","uid":136663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00236568a6e30af5232d7d7ba3e83dd1e6937337","tid":365862,"uid":136663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老味</span><br />\n人哋做少少嘢令你唔順超就屌到飛天<br />\n你自己做錯嘢就大條道理自圓其說<br />\n我真係仆你個街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做嘢做到咁乸西仲好意思話：其實都唔差啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心你唔好繼續喺度獻世<br />\n唔該將你啲垃圾雙重標準塞返入你個死人口度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再借我過橋嚟增強你啲自信心啊你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8ca2384d65571cc567969ff575e8c688cff160f4","tid":365862,"uid":10687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:40:36.000Z","msg":"read"},{"pid":"f9e72029d432060602693f298f31fc91b2238dd9","tid":365862,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"不如你再講白啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35e2a730208be8de39f6f034d229f82be83c89b","tid":365862,"uid":59465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"即係樓主自己廢<br />\n當面俾人屌個時就唔敢還口<br />\n事後唔甘心就上網求認同<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"843bd323ee4926a422ebafe2004093916cf357b7","tid":365862,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"岩啊，你背曬段野之後鬧佢"}]}